make-page-responsive/twitter.html.body:
Twitter Feed
Poh is a very social animal so he wants to share his twitter with everyone

Note Make a twitter feed section for your website using the Twitter Publish tool
Put the generated code for the twitter feed into a column that is 8 wide, using an offset to centre the feed on the page
